

                     (Caution :- Before you use this tool make sure your bluetooth adapter is working or not)
                       
         
         Step 1 :- Start your bluetooth service (sudo systemctl start bluetooth).
         
         Step 2 :- Scan to find bluetooth devices (sudo hcitool -i hci1 scan). 
         
         Step 3 :- Run the script inside the noctraptor folder (sudo python3 silent_test.py  < Target device MAC address >).

         Step 4 :- After the script runs wait for a while to capture the RAW audio packets for recording.
         
         Step 5 :- As per the users timimg (press ctrl c) to stop the tool. 
         
         Step 6 :- Run (ls) to find your saved recording.
         
         Step 7 :- Play the saved audio by running (aplay file_name.wav).
         
         
                 (Note :- This tool will only work on bluetooth devices like :- speakers,earbuds,headphones,neckbands)
                 
                 
                               (It will not work on android phones/iphones and smart watches)             
                           
                           
          




							       
							      
